On the browser side you might want to take a look at Dojo&#39;s REST
capabilities. REST concepts are deeply integrated into Dojo, it has a
uniform interface called the Dojo Data, and utilizes a JsonRestStore
for RESTful communication with servers. We have a lot of developers
using it with a wide variety of servers.
Kris

